text: <@U0UFDAS91>: yes indeed.  <@U16Q0J0E6> I failed to draw your attention to this post: <https://hyperledgerproject.slack.com/archives/identity/p1462503188000094>, where I hopefully didn't mischaracterize you too badly.  It would be good to get your reaction to it.  I'm particularly interested to know where I can see the most up-to-date descriptions of the overview you gave at the F2F (assuming I am correct that the protocol-spec document isn't it).  Thanks.  It was great meeting you and learning from you!
